#: en/content/installation/packages.xml:156 en/content/installation/packages.xml:380
msgid ""
"Now you can start the OTRS daemon and activate corresponding watchdog cron "
"job (this must be done by the <literal>otrs</literal> user): <placeholder "
"type=\"screen\" id=\"0\"/> That's it, congratulations!"
