#: en/content/installation/packages.xml:188
msgid ""
"Install MySQL by executing the following command as root: <placeholder "
"type=\"screen\" id=\"0\"/> This will install MySQL with the default options "
"on your system. You'll need to change the defaults in order to make it "
"suitable for OTRS. With a text editor open the file "
